    "body": "## Problem:\r\nFields (key names) in classes, keysets, and quasi-keysets are ordered randomly, which adds friction when reading (and updating) docs.\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\n- Sort class fields and keysets when generating docs.\r\n- Add a lint check for quasi-keysets (keysets defined as unstructured  markdown lists within a docstring).\r\n\r\n## Disclosure ⚠️ 🚀 🤖 \r\n\r\nThis PR was AI-assisted in order to avoid human slop. Say no to human slop 🥺.",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-26T18:39:29Z",
